channel.title: Language problem
channel.description:
this is my 3rd source ive downloaded cause every1 I open any of the files with notepad wanting to take a look at what I got and it is not readable. Like not English at all lol. At first I was thinking it was developers anti-leech but after it being on all 3 sources I got I figured I screwed something up making it come up like this. ima try n upload a picture and see if some1 can help me get it all back to English please so its readable :o I really wanna use this source to learn how to do some beginner coding (:

Might have to like copy paste onto paint and use mag. glass to see it better but that's just the shop handler file.... Every single file is like that, client,server, characters, ect.. :/
Please help

Listen to lil_smok3r… you’re opening the .class files instead of the .java files.

You have to be careful because each .java file have a corresponding .class file with the same exact name so look at the file ext. before trying to code it.
